title: Idaho prep volleyball: Bonners Ferry stays alive - Thu, 22 Oct 2015 PST
text:
Kadi Bateman finished with 22 assists and two aces, while Miranda Wenk added 11 kills Thursday as host Bonners Ferry defeated Kellogg 3-1 in a loser-out match of the 3A District I volleyball tournament. 
The Badgers will play a state play-in match on Saturday in Grangeville.
